---
import BaseLayout from '../layout/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout tittle='FAQs'>
  <section class='py-16 px-4 lg:px-24 bg-gray-50'>
    <div class='max-w-6xl mx-auto'>
      <div class='grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start'>
        <!-- Left Intro -->
        <div>
          <h2 class='text-4xl font-bold text-[#074351] mb-6'>
            Frequently Asked Questions
          </h2>
          <p class='text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6'>
            Find quick answers about ICAN’s mission, programs, and how you can
            support our community efforts. Still have questions? Get in touch
            with us anytime.
          </p>
          <a
            href='/about-us/contact'
            class='inline-block btn-primary font-medium px-6 py-3 rounded-lg shadow transition'>
            Contact Us
          </a>
        </div>

        <!-- Right Accordion (Flowbite) -->
        <div
          id='accordion-collapse'
          data-accordion='collapse'
          class='space-y-4'>
          <div
            class='border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm aria-expanded:bg-[#185a69]'>
            <h2 id='accordion-collapse-heading-1'>
              <button
                type='button'
                class='flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 text-left text-lg font-medium aria-expanded:bg-[#185a69]'
                data-accordion-target='#accordion-collapse-body-1'
                aria-expanded='true'
                aria-controls='accordion-collapse-body-1'>
                What is ICAN?
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class='w-5 h-5 shrink-0'
                  fill='currentColor'
                  viewBox='0 0 20 20'
                  ><path
                    fill-rule='evenodd'
                    d='M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 10.939l3.71-3.71a.75.75 0 111.06 1.06l-4.24 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.06 0L5.25 8.27a.75.75 0 01-.02-1.06z'
                    clip-rule='evenodd'></path></svg
                >
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id='accordion-collapse-body-1'
              class='hidden'
              aria-labelledby='accordion-collapse-heading-1'>
              <div class='px-6 pb-4 text-gray-700'>
                ICAN, or the Inuana Community Action Network, is a youth-led
                nonprofit organization in Homa Bay, Kenya. We’re committed to
                community empowerment through health, sustainability, and
                youth-focused programs.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm'>
            <h2 id='accordion-collapse-heading-2'>
              <button
                type='button'
                class='flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 text-left text-[#074351] text-lg font-medium aria-expanded:bg-[#185a69]'
                data-accordion-target='#accordion-collapse-body-2'
                aria-expanded='false'
                aria-controls='accordion-collapse-body-2'>
                How did ICAN start?
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class='w-5 h-5 shrink-0'
                  fill='currentColor'
                  viewBox='0 0 20 20'
                  ><path
                    fill-rule='evenodd'
                    d='M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 10.939l3.71-3.71a.75.75 0 111.06 1.06l-4.24 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.06 0L5.25 8.27a.75.75 0 01-.02-1.06z'
                    clip-rule='evenodd'></path></svg
                >
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id='accordion-collapse-body-2'
              class='hidden'
              aria-labelledby='accordion-collapse-heading-2'>
              <div class='px-6 pb-4 text-gray-700'>
                ICAN began as a small local youth initiative in Homa Bay and
                evolved into a registered organization through the efforts of
                passionate young people dedicated to community transformation.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm'>
            <h2 id='accordion-collapse-heading-3'>
              <button
                type='button'
                class='flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 text-left text-[#074351] text-lg font-medium aria-expanded:bg-[#185a69]'
                data-accordion-target='#accordion-collapse-body-3'
                aria-expanded='false'
                aria-controls='accordion-collapse-body-3'>
                How can I support ICAN’s work?
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class='w-5 h-5 shrink-0'
                  fill='currentColor'
                  viewBox='0 0 20 20'
                  ><path
                    fill-rule='evenodd'
                    d='M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 10.939l3.71-3.71a.75.75 0 111.06 1.06l-4.24 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.06 0L5.25 8.27a.75.75 0 01-.02-1.06z'
                    clip-rule='evenodd'></path></svg
                >
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id='accordion-collapse-body-3'
              class='hidden'
              aria-labelledby='accordion-collapse-heading-3'>
              <div class='px-6 pb-4 text-gray-700'>
                You can support ICAN by making a donation, becoming a monthly
                donor, volunteering, or partnering with us on initiatives
                aligned with our mission.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm'>
            <h2 id='accordion-collapse-heading-4'>
              <button
                type='button'
                class='flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 text-left text-[#074351] text-lg font-medium aria-expanded:bg-[#185a69]'
                data-accordion-target='#accordion-collapse-body-4'
                aria-expanded='false'
                aria-controls='accordion-collapse-body-4'>
                Where does ICAN operate?
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class='w-5 h-5 shrink-0'
                  fill='currentColor'
                  viewBox='0 0 20 20'
                  ><path
                    fill-rule='evenodd'
                    d='M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 10.939l3.71-3.71a.75.75 0 111.06 1.06l-4.24 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.06 0L5.25 8.27a.75.75 0 01-.02-1.06z'
                    clip-rule='evenodd'></path></svg
                >
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id='accordion-collapse-body-4'
              class='hidden'
              aria-labelledby='accordion-collapse-heading-4'>
              <div class='px-6 pb-4 text-gray-700'>
                ICAN operates primarily in Homa Bay County, Kenya, but we
                collaborate with national and international partners to expand
                our impact.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <div class='border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-sm'>
            <h2 id='accordion-collapse-heading-5'>
              <button
                type='button'
                class='flex items-center justify-between w-full px-6 py-4 text-left text-[#074351] text-lg font-medium aria-expanded:bg-[#185a69]'
                data-accordion-target='#accordion-collapse-body-5'
                aria-expanded='false'
                aria-controls='accordion-collapse-body-5'>
                Can I volunteer or partner with ICAN?
                <svg
                  data-accordion-icon
                  class='w-5 h-5 shrink-0'
                  fill='currentColor'
                  viewBox='0 0 20 20'
                  ><path
                    fill-rule='evenodd'
                    d='M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 10.939l3.71-3.71a.75.75 0 111.06 1.06l-4.24 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.06 0L5.25 8.27a.75.75 0 01-.02-1.06z'
                    clip-rule='evenodd'></path></svg
                >
              </button>
            </h2>
            <div
              id='accordion-collapse-body-5'
              class='hidden'
              aria-labelledby='accordion-collapse-heading-5'>
              <div class='px-6 pb-4 text-gray-700'>
                Absolutely! We welcome volunteers and partners. Please reach out
                via our Contact page to explore current opportunities.
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- AlpineJS CDN -->
  <script
    src='https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/alpinejs@3.x.x/dist/cdn.min.js'
    defer></script>
</BaseLayout>
